{"tid":973341,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民親中出賣香港先係焦土派","createTime":"2019-01-08T05:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T10:18:13.000Z","uid":47359,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d38339026841add274c248a451d10e752599ed","tid":973341,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:33:51.000Z","msg":"有票唔投唔阻止惡法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nsHrNk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nsHrNk.png&h=21d2b4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年6月17日，沙中線8.47億追加撥款以6票之差獲得通過，10名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F162225&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5bf0d5c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年3月22日，立法會審議 1131億臨時撥款，在全體泛民議員缺席下，議案只花兩分鐘，由不足十名建制派議員在不記名投票下贊成通過。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180322%2Fbkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0e949a1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月26日，工務小組審議17.85億元朗行人天橋撥款，議案以3票之差獲得通過，5名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fresults%2Fv201805261.pdf&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=627d32ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月25日，林卓廷提出就「升降機維修保養對市民安全進行辯論議案」以6票之差未獲通過，7名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fhc%2Fvoting%2Fhc20180525-voting-ec.pdf&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3ade9afd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月31日，建制派「共建粵港澳大灣區」動議順利通過，地方選區輸2票，2名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fvoting%2Fv20180530.pdf&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a91a35d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"7d20a3b7cf56516a0081cb64802d21e81b524f0b","tid":973341,"uid":175623,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"泛民成日都以為自己好decent<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地諗野太離地啦<br />\n連我都對佢地心死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24380a0e81241504c1698cb992b0168edd5b8761","tid":973341,"uid":161168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e0774d92fdfac32f2eb308a3a2dff0235d744c","tid":973341,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:33:10.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"a70892599533eff370874f32e47ac6d009aff084","tid":973341,"uid":226955,"li